        "text": "Jonah 4:9",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). How many a holy work of household and parish has been and is thus hindered and destroyed; and if the golden words of the first bishop of the Church had been heeded better, there never had appeared one page of her long history blotted with the blood of a religious war.",
