        "class": "",
        "text": " I. ed. 1, p. 548 f.), finds expressed in the words of James, that “one by wrathful zeal effects not ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "on others",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
