        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Romans 1:17",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " and here, to consist in this, that Paul speaks of justification, in James of regeneration, the untenableness of his explanation is the more evident, for that ",
        "children": []
