      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Timothy 2:8",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; and its actions, whether just or unjust, are more widely exposed to view. The wrath here intimated is that of nature, without grace.—",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "δικαιοσύνην Θεοῦ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
